          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="animation-element bounce-up cf">
          <div class="card learn">
            <div class="content">
              <h2 class="title">Learn</h2>
              <p class="copy">For those who are new to Data Science, Plotify provides step-by-step tutorials. Learn
                thorugh tutorials and Experiment on your data.</p>
              <button class="btn btn-dark" onclick="location.href='/tutorial'">Tutorials</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-dark py-4" style="width: 100%;margin-top: 100px;">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <p class="text-muted mb-0 py-2">Â© 2021 Plotify All rights reserved.</p>
